---
import SectionLabel from "./SectionLabel.astro";
import { formatShortDate, github } from "~/data/github";
---

<section class="reveal" id="about">
  <SectionLabel index="01" label="about" cmd="cat README.md" glyph="人" />
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] gap-4">
    <article class="win">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-border bg-fg text-panel px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">
        <span>// chapter 01 / opening monologue</span>
        <span>est. 2024</span>
      </div>
      <div class="win-body text-[13px] sm:text-[0.95rem] leading-snug sm:leading-relaxed text-fg-dim space-y-2.5 sm:space-y-3.5">
        <p>
          Hey, I'm <span class="font-bold text-fg">Hunter</span>. I build small,
          fast software solo: browser games, real-time multiplayer, Rust TUIs,
          and native macOS utilities.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most of what's on this page started as a tool I wished existed — a
          tighter aim trainer, a 10&nbsp;KB game I could play on a phone, a
          contribution heatmap that lives in the terminal. Weekend prototype,
          a week of daily-driving, a tighter rewrite if it earns its slot.
        </p>
        <p>
          The browser games run on plain canvas + websockets. The TUIs are
          Rust + Ratatui. The macOS utilities are SwiftUI/AppKit, no Electron.
          Everything ships, then keeps getting smaller.
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-fg pt-1 border-t border-border">
          <span>$</span> currently shipping: <a href="https://coup.chuds.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ink-link">coup</a>, <a href="https://aim.chuds.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ink-link">hudaim</a>, <a href="https://ant.chuds.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ink-link">antmaze</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <aside class="border border-border bg-panel flex flex-col">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-border bg-fg text-panel px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase shrink-0">
        <span>// recent activity</span>
        <span>feed</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 font-mono text-xs p-4 screentone flex-1 min-h-0 md:overflow-hidden md:[mask-image:linear-gradient(to_bottom,black_calc(100%-2.5rem),transparent)]">
        {github.recentActivity.slice(0, 12).map((item, idx) => (
          <li class:list={[
            "grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto] gap-3 border-b border-border pb-2 last:border-b-0 last:pb-0",
            idx >= 4 && "hidden md:grid",
          ]}>
            <span class="truncate min-w-0">{item.label}</span>
            <span class="text-fg-muted shrink-0">{formatShortDate(item.at)}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
